Create a setup wizard where the user need to input the School name and other need information.
It will create a record and check if the information already provided if not show the wizard page first.
Ask the user for
1. School name
2. Address
3. Contact information
4. Logo

During the wizard setup the admin account must be auto created.
username : admin
password : admin1234

The login page when the page is rendered must be display only when the need information above already provided otherwise keep showing the wizard page.

Allow this api to be access without authorization